                <h1>Mary Kay Ash: The Empowering Beauty Entrepreneur</h1>
                <p>Mary Kay Ash was a pioneering entrepreneur who founded Mary Kay Cosmetics in 1963. Her vision was to empower women through business opportunities and quality skincare products. Ash inspired countless individuals by promoting a supportive culture and a strong sales strategy, making her a prominent figure in the beauty industry.</p>
